metadata.name: Retro Reptilian 1 : The Master Chief
metadata.description:
Nobody could predict the arrival of the Retro Reptilians, except the self-generated metaverse (by a reptilian AI) from which they came. Their creation begins with the head, from a fountain of LSD that appeared in the middle of a huge digital rocky desert.

This first creation reveals their pack leader, the only Retro Reptilian with horns, who will guide them, if they manage to escape from their virtual world, in taking control of humanity.
